column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday April 12 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: Roadway shutdown between N Yarnallton Pike and Browns Mill Rd (near Scott Co line) until further notice.  Serious injury collision.
Inbound traffic diverted to Browns Mill Rd toward Old Frankfort Pike.
Outbound traffic diverted to N Yarnallton Pike and may use Bethel Rd to Paynes Depot Rd.
